data.subject: SDXL Resolution Presets (ws)
data.question: What does the SDXL Resolution Presets custom node offer for ComfyUI?
data.answer: The SDXL Resolution Presets custom node provides easy access to the officially supported resolutions in both horizontal and vertical formats.

data.subject: SDXL Resolution Presets (ws)
data.question: Which resolutions are available in the SDXL Resolution Presets custom node?
data.answer: The resolutions available in the SDXL Resolution Presets custom node are 1024x1024, 1152x896, 1216x832, 1344x768, and 1536x640.

data.subject: SDXL Resolution Presets (ws)
data.question: Does the SDXL Resolution Presets custom node support landscape and portrait formats?
data.answer: Yes, the SDXL Resolution Presets custom node supports both horizontal and vertical formats, which includes both landscape and portrait orientations.

data.subject: SDXL Resolution Presets (ws)
data.question: How can I utilize the SDXL Resolution Presets in ComfyUI?
data.answer: To use the SDXL Resolution Presets in ComfyUI, you would navigate to this custom node within the ComfyUI interface and select the desired resolution from the provided options.
